          {
            "title": "Intro",
            "id": 126825,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Vamos aprender um novo conceito que explica como variáveis acompanham coisas como adicionar ou remover dólares de uma carteira.</p><webview version=\"2\" content=\"&lt;!doctype html&gt;&#xA;&lt;html&gt;&#xA; &lt;head&gt;&#xA;  &lt;style&gt;&#xA;   button {&#xA;    background-color: darkBlue;&#xA;    /* Green */&#xA;    border: none;&#xA;    border-radius: 8px;&#xA;    color: white;&#xA;    text-align: center;&#xA;    text-decoration: none;&#xA;    display: inline-block;&#xA;    font-size: 14px;&#xA;    padding: 6px 12px;&#xA;    margin: 0 12px 0 0;&#xA;   }&#xA;  &lt;/style&gt;&#xA; &lt;/head&gt;&#xA; &lt;body&gt;&#xA;  &lt;h1&gt;Wallet: &lt;strong&gt;$&lt;span id=&quot;amount&quot;&gt;15&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;  &lt;button onclick=&quot;add()&quot;&gt;Add $1&lt;/button&gt;&#xA;  &lt;button onclick=&quot;remove()&quot;&gt;Remove $1&lt;/button&gt;&#xA;  &lt;script&gt;&#xA;   var wallet = 15;&#xA;   let amountCounter = document.getElementById('amount');&#xA;   &#xA;   function add() {&#xA;    wallet += 1;&#xA;    amountCounter.innerHTML = wallet;&#xA;   }&#xA;   &#xA;   function remove() {&#xA;    wallet -= 1;&#xA;    amountCounter.innerHTML = wallet;&#xA;   }&#xA;  &lt;/script&gt;&#xA; &lt;/body&gt;&#xA;&lt;/html&gt;\" /></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Assigning a value",
            "id": 126826,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Quando criamos uma variável, nós <strong>atribuímos</strong> a ela um valor, como atribuir <code>3</code> a <code>wallet</code>.</p><code name=\"main.swift\" version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" wallet = \" /><text value=\"3\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(wallet)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"===\" /></content></option><option startIndex=\"11\" endIndex=\"12\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"3\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>=</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Self-assigning a value",
            "id": 126827,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p><strong>Atribuição a si mesmo</strong> é quando definimos uma variável usando ela mesma. Por exemplo, podemos definir <code>wallet</code> para seu valor <code>3</code> mais <code>1</code> com <code>wallet = wallet + 1</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"var\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" wallet = \" /><text value=\"3\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"wallet = wallet + \" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(wallet)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"15\" endIndex=\"21\" /><option startIndex=\"22\" endIndex=\"23\" /><option startIndex=\"24\" endIndex=\"34\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"4\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>wallet</code> seguido de <code>=</code> e finalmente <code>wallet + 1</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Incrementing numbers",
            "id": 126828,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Como podemos auto-atribuir variáveis, podemos aumentar ou diminuir variáveis definidas como números. Tente aumentar <code>wallet</code> com <code>wallet = wallet + 1</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"var\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" wallet = \" /><text value=\"3\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"wallet = wallet + \" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(wallet)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"24\" endIndex=\"34\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"3 + 1\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"4\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>wallet + 1</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Why self-assigning matters",
            "id": 126829,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Variáveis auto-atribuídas nos permitem rastrear dados que mudam ao longo do tempo. Por exemplo, um usuário pode adicionar <code>2</code> dólares a uma carteira e depois remover <code>1</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"var\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" wallet = \" /><text value=\"3\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"wallet = wallet + \" /><text value=\"2\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"wallet = wallet - \" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(wallet)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"33\" endIndex=\"34\" /><option startIndex=\"53\" endIndex=\"54\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"4\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>2</code> seguido de <code>1</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Self-assigning strings",
            "id": 126830,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Variáveis definidas como strings funcionam da mesma maneira. Tente definir <code>nameInfo</code> como <code>nameInfo + \" John\"</code>.</p><code name=\"main.swift\" version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\"><content><text value=\"var\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" nameInfo = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Account name:&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"nameInfo = nameInfo + \" /><text value=\"&quot; Elton&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"nameInfo = nameInfo + \" /><text value=\"&quot; John&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(nameInfo)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"73\" endIndex=\"81\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Account name: Elton John\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>nameInfo</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: Assigning a value",
            "id": 126831,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Qual é o valor atribuído à variável <code>speed</code>?</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" speed = \" /><text value=\"0\" class=\"number\" /></content></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\"><code>0</code></item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\"><code>speed</code></item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>0</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: Incrementing numbers",
            "id": 126833,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>O que este código exibe no console?</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"var\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" speed = \" /><text value=\"100\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"speed = speed + \" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(speed)\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"101\" /></content></output></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\"><code>101</code></item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\"><code>100</code></item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>101</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: Why self-assigning matters",
            "id": 126834,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Por que a auto-atribuição é um conceito de programação tão poderoso?</p><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">Porque nos permite rastrear dados que mudam ao longo do tempo</item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">Porque isso nos ajuda a criar comparações</item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Porque nos permite rastrear dados que mudam ao longo do tempo.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: Self-assigning strings",
            "id": 126835,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>O que este código exibe no console?</p><code name=\"main.swift\" version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\"><content><text value=\"var\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" fullName = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Jane&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"fullName = fullName + \" /><text value=\"&quot; Bowling&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(fullName)\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"Jane Bowling\" /></content></output></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\"><code>Jane Bowling</code></item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\"><code>Bowling Jane</code></item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\"><code>Jane Bowling</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Assigning a value",
            "id": 126836,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Atribua <code>15</code> à constante <code>wallet</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" wallet = \" /><text value=\"15\" class=\"number\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"11\" endIndex=\"12\" /><option startIndex=\"13\" endIndex=\"15\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"===\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>=</code> seguido de <code>15</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Self-assigning a value",
            "id": 126837,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Atribua um valor a <code>likes</code> para que <code>5</code> seja exibido no console.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" number = \" /><text value=\"5\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" likes = number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(likes)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"27\" endIndex=\"33\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"6\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"7\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"5\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>number</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Incrementing numbers",
            "id": 126838,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Adicione cinco ao valor da variável <code>inventory</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"var\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" inventory = \" /><text value=\"11\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"inventory = inventory + \" /><text value=\"5\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(inventory)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"31\" endIndex=\"44\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"5\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"16\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>inventory + 5</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Why self-assigning matters",
            "id": 126839,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Subtraia um do valor da variável <code>cards</code>, depois adicione quatro.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"var\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" cards = \" /><text value=\"3\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"cards = cards - \" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"cards = cards + \" /><text value=\"4\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(cards)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"28\" endIndex=\"29\" /><option startIndex=\"30\" endIndex=\"31\" /><option startIndex=\"46\" endIndex=\"47\" /><option startIndex=\"48\" endIndex=\"49\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"6\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>-</code> seguido de <code>1</code> e depois <code>+</code>, <code>4</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
